       Official Source (packs that reference the official file by
       download — e.g. CurseForge/Modrinth pack manifests — satisfy this
       automatically);
     - you do not present the Mod as your own work; and
     - the pack's listing credits "Nerospace by Neroland" with links to
       the CurseForge page above and the GitHub repository
       (<https://github.com/Neroland/nerospace>).

c) CONTENT CREATION & COMMERCIAL USE. Create and monetise videos, streams,
